    "title": {
      "rendered": "Five Recent LinkedIn Group Updates Nonprofits Need to Know About"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14220\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof-300x296.jpg?resize=300%2C296\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof.jpg?resize=300%2C296&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-Groups-for-Nonprof.jpg?w=405&amp;ssl=1 405w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>With the launch of <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=1172477\">new a LinkedIn Groups design</a>, the company resolved one of its most pressing problems\u00a0\u2013\u00a0LinkedIn Group spam. Group management had become cumbersome and time-consuming for many admins of medium and large groups. Flagging irrelevant discussions as promotion posts or deleting them altogether can take up to thirty minutes a day and if you didn&#8217;t invest the time to get rid of the clutter, then the group would become overrun with spam and lose its appeal to group members. The new design, however, requires people to participate if they want their discussions to get noticed. The mass posting of links as discussions will likely still continue, but without participation, the links won&#8217;t achieve &#8220;Popular&#8221; status.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Featured Hero Image</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-11.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14212\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn for Nonprofits 1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-11.png?resize=600%2C323\" width=\"600\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-11.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-11.png?resize=300%2C161&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-32.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14203\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn for Nonprofits 3\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-32.png?resize=600%2C219\" width=\"600\" height=\"219\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-32.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-32.png?resize=300%2C109&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n2. Increased Spam Control: Popular and Recent Discussion Tabs</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-82.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14217\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn for Nonprofits 8\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-82.png?resize=600%2C519\" width=\"600\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-82.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-82.png?resize=300%2C259&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n3. Manager&#8217;s Choice Selections Prominently Featured</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-2.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14204\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn for Nonprofits 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-2.png?resize=600%2C194\" width=\"600\" height=\"194\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-2.png?resize=300%2C97&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n4. New Group Information Pop-down</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-5.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14206\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"LinkedIn for Nonprofits 5\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-5.png?resize=600%2C171\" width=\"600\" height=\"171\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-5.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/LinkedIn-for-Nonprofits-5.png?resize=300%2C85&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n5. Mobile-Compatible</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/linkedin-groups-mobile.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14219\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"linkedin groups mobile\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/linkedin-groups-mobile.png?resize=400%2C600\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/linkedin-groups-mobile.png?w=400&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/linkedin-groups-mobile.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\nRelated Webinar:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/webinar-linkedin-groups-and-company-pages-for-nonprofits/\">LinkedIn Groups and Company Pages for Nonprofits</a></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
